<br>
1. No changes to the current melee/aggro/disc/skill caps/spells etc will ever be made again<br>
<br>
2. Level and number of aa's stays the same (aa's go to unspend obviously).<br>
<br>
3. All gear is transfered or changed to equivalent for the new class (ie. warrior has eyepatch of plunder you change to pally, pally has eyepatch, warrior has uber weapons new shadow knight has equivalent uber weapons (could change 2 1 handers for a 2hander etc.)<br>
<br>
4. Get to keep the same name and anything special about your char, just change the class (and race if needed)<br>
<br>
Since this is a warrior board and we are tanks the only options are the other 2 tank classes,  any paladin's or shadow knights who read these boards could post and change to a warrior or the other knight.<br>
<br>
I realize this serves no purpose and would result in a ton of level 65 gimps and of coure will never happen but I am curious of what class would like to change to what and which of the 3 tanks would be the most popular.  <br>
<br>
Please don't turn this into a class envy thread as we have enoguh of them.  Responses should be short and of the following format:<br>
<br>
Level 60 Warrior<br>
change to Shadow knight<br>
<br>
OR<br>
<br>
Level 59 Paladin <br>
No change<br>
<br>
OR<br>
<br>
Level 65 shadow knight<br>
change to Warrior<br>
<br>
Please don't give reasons or comments just simply post level, current class and what one you would change to if you could or if you wouldn't change at all. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=kiyallmanebloodcry>KiyallmaneBloodcry</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>will kick your @$$</span><br>  Posts: 467<br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/9/03 1:52 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1974.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.earthlink.net/~bass72/_uimages/Kiya2.GIF hieght=140 width=113></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Would You Switch if you could?</span><hr size=1> 60 Warrior<br>
