<br>
I say this really because of one main issue, and that's warrior stackability. I'm not in an uberguild, but because of the relationship of my guild with the #2 guild on our server, I have access to pretty much any content on the server and some pretty decent gear has started to come my way. Not the top of the line, but at the level of play I'm at, the castoffs of a top tier guild are a pretty big upgrade, hehe. I'm also flagged for every zone but time and the factory floor of poi.<br>
<br>
The problem is one of stackability. I love being a warrior. I love the hp. I love the pure tank concept and it's why I chose the class and continue to trudge on. The thing is, we have 6 warriors in my guild that are basically all at the same level as I, 2 others very close and another is proposed for membership who's also about the same. 2, including this new proposed members have an edge in terms of aa pts, and I have an edge in gear and hp's on most of the others. Because of our numbers, I rarely get to be the MT and there is quite a bit of dilution of the loot pool as there are alot of guys to equip.<br>
<br>
The uber guild I am fortunate enough to be able to raid with has a cadre of warriors that are all, of course, much further along that I. This makes playing a warrior very frustrating at times. We have no other special bells and whistles but our tanking ability, and in xp groups that isn't even all that special. I also hate that we, without some luck and some very specific gear, get owned by just about every class in pvp even when skill levels arent equal. Resists really don't matter that much any more with all the lure based attacks out there and warriors lack any big ticket multiple k attacks which limits our utility in raids if we don't tank, experience groups pretty much all the time, and in pvp all the time.<br>
<br>
I still have misguided hope that they may add to our class some time in the future, and I sure as hell am not going to reroll my character at this point. I love being a warrior and would only change under the circumstances listed originally.<br>
<br>
peace,<br>
Aielman KajiraLiege<br>
Shining Alliance, Prexus <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://members.aol.com/azarielleeq/images/aieldon.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><br>
