<br>
Originally necros till the nerfs, then went druid, frustrated at a lack of a raid role, they rolled either monks or warriors, and are likely out there rolling shamans, wizards, rangers or knights now.   <br>
<br>
The swing will come again, and they will continually feel &quot;victimized&quot; but have no one to blame but their own inability to focus, and ride through hard times.<br>
